        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <h3 class="article__title">Cyber</h3>
          <p class="para-block">In a world which is more connected than ever before, cyber threats are becoming more common and increasingly sophisticated. While facing a cyber-attack, organizations need to respond swiftly to minimise the threat and damage while safeguarding their critical information infrastructure. After a cyber-security breach, swift response and expert forensic investigation enable organizations to recover quickly by reducing exposure, recovering data, and deploying appropriate security measures.</p>
          <p class="para-block">At Arceus Consulting, we are specialists in Cyber Security Incident Response and Digital Forensics. Our team of cyber and forensic experts provide comprehensive, and technology driven solutions that identify the root cause of attacks and suggest implementable measures to stop the reoccurrence of such security breaches.</p>
          <p class="para-block bold">Arceus Consulting is an Indian Judiciary approved organization. Forensic reports and evidence collected by us are for our clients are official and admissible in the court of law.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-break image-dual">
        <img src="../images/cyber-break-1.jpeg">
        <img src="../images/cyber-break-2.jpeg">
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left"></div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <p class="para-title">Incidence Response</p>
          <p class="para-block">After a cyber-attack, organizations need to eradicate the adversary from the system immediately, identify the compromised systems, and assess the data exposed, leaked, and exfiltrated. Arceus Consulting’s team of cyber and forensic experts act swiftly and timely to mitigate the damage caused by the attack. We leverage cyber tools to dig deep into the attack and understand the severity of the threat and the data at risk. Through our services, we help address various parameters of the cyber threat and assist your organization by providing a proactive assessment of current threats and how to mitigate them through process improvements.</p>
          <p class="para-title">Resilience Solution</p>
          <p class="para-block">Arceus Consulting provides containment solutions to reduce the impact of an incident. Through our cyber capabilities and expertise, our team limits the impact of the attack on the systems and networks affected. Our consultants work closely with the management by prioritizing, planning, and executing the securing of the networks and systems. After containing the threat, we assist our clients in restoring their network infrastructure and systems to resume their business operations normally.</p>
          <p class="para-title">Red Teaming</p>
          <p class="para-block">Arceus Consulting helps to prepare your organization for real cyber-attacks through our Red Teaming services. We help improve your organization’s and personnel’s preparedness to mitigate by performing a realistic security incident scenario that targets your organization’s cyber and physical assets and security elements. We tailor every attack scenario to a specific objective for your organization’s needs. Through this, we flag critical functions of your organization that can be compromised in an attack, therefore, causing severe damage to your assets, regulatory compliance, or reputation. Arceus Consulting also provides Red Teaming services for individuals to safeguard them from potential cyber-attacks through their assets such as devices, social media, email ids, digital networks, etc.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-break image-single">
        <img src="../images/cyber-break-3.jpeg">
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left"></div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <p class="para-title">Uncovering and Mitigating Negative Campaigns</p>
          <p class="para-block">With the advent of social media, organizations and individuals (HNIs) are increasingly coming under threat from adversaries operating using alias identities or anonymously on social media and other public digital forums. Campaigns run through blogs, news articles, comments, videos, and pictures with negative intent on social media have severe effects on the reputation of a brand or an individual. Arceus Consulting mitigates the damage caused by the negative campaigns being run over our clients by discovering the attackers' identity, motivation, bias, and conflict.</p>
          <p class="para-title">Ransomware</p>
          <p class="para-block">Ransomware has become a significant threat for organizations and individuals globally. Attackers can encrypt or erase files on the infected system/network or block access to the systems and demand ransom to unlock them. Arceus Consulting helps its clients to get their data back completely without paying the ransomware to the attackers. Our team comprises specialist cyber experts with extensive experience in successfully handling ransomware cases and recovering our clients' data and compromised systems.</p>
          <p class="para-title">Forensics</p>
          <p class="para-block">Arceus Consulting is an approved Indian Judiciary cyber evidence reporter. The testimonies and reports provided by us are valid and official in all the courts in India. Our forensic capabilities include DNA Mapping, DNA Footprinting, Document Forgery Analysis, and Audio and Video Forensics.
            <ul>
              <li>
                <p class="para-title">Digital Forensics</p>
                <p class="para-block">Leveraging our cyber expertise, we identify when and how files have been altered or manipulated, help legal teams to gather digital and forensic evidence, and establish timelines and patterns of behaviour. Furthermore, we assess and analyse audio and video files to verify their legitimacy and find tampering.</p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p class="para-title">Mobile Phone Forensics and Computer Forensics</p>
                <p class="para-block">Arceus Consulting provides forensic services to recover, clone, transfer, and secure data on mobile phones, tablets, laptops, hard drives, computers, etc. We work closely with regulatory and enforcement bodies regularly to assist them with forensic services during investigations. Being an Indian Judiciary cyber evidence reporter, Arceus Consulting also provides testimony to the court of law during investigations.</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="para-title">Cyberbullying</p>
          <p class="para-block">Cyberbullying harassment over digital platforms, especially social media is done to threaten, insult, or embarrass individuals. It is a form of abuse in which attackers share or negative or false content to harm or humiliate target individuals. At Arceus Consulting, our team of expert anti-cyberbullying consultants helps you by tracing attackers and eliminating their attacks. We track down attackers through our cyber expertise and social engineering skills, take down their websites instantly, and launch counter cyber attacks to nullify the harm being caused.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
